Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:01.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やけに蟲が騒がしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺を喰う気なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐れているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや ただ　見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が何なのか　探ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうやら　人の子ではあるようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,緑の目玉に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,白い髪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前の噂　聞いてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲を寄せる体質を持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,歩く地に災いをもたらす異形の子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何度か蟲師に拾われたと聞くが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また厄介払いでもされたか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なぜ蟲を寄せるままにしておく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:31.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一つ所に留まらなければ 災いは防げるだろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,食ってくためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が蟲を寄せて　蟲師が治す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:44.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それが時々　手に負えねぇことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:50.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前を拾ったのはそういう輩ばかりってわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺はスグロ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山で蟲師をやってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:07.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほぉ　この窩にトコヤミがとらわれている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　トコヤミに呑まれたことがあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それで体質が変わっちまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,トコヤミ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,他の蟲師は言わなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,闇の姿をした蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ある時期から昔の記憶がないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは記憶も喰う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　それを取り出せば　この体質もなくなるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつはお前にとらわれてるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,トコヤミが蟲を寄せるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲を寄せるのは　あくまでお前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういう者は稀にいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それを治す術は誰も持たない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気の毒だが　受け入れるほかない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まぁ　蟲は散らしておいた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,数日はもつだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また行き倒れんよう　体力つけていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは光脈筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　あれはヌシか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなに見張らずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここに居座ったりはしねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,歩けそうなら　付いてこい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,基本的な薬草ぐらいは覚えたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,多少は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山の草は薬効が高い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いくらか持ってけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲除けの煙草の作り方も覚えていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,周囲への影響を弱めるだけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前自身を蟲患いから守ってもくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,美しいところだろう　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,長居はさせてやれんが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:10.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,たまに訪ねるぐらいなら　ヌシ殿も文句は言うまいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やあ　スグロ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見かけねぇ子供連れてんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:32.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや何　少しの間面倒を見ることになった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まぁ　弟子みたいなもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　挨拶しねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それは　しっかりやんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ところで　どうだ 新しいヌシのほうは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　まだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう生まれてもいいんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なぁに　心配要らねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:04.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,我々が心配せずとも　毎年花は咲くし　実をつける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それが「理」というものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,新しいヌシって　どういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヌシにも寿命ってもんはある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山のヌシは　もうかなりの老齢でな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:36.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　まだ次のヌシらしきものが見当たらない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヌシの座に空白ができれば　山は荒む
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それをみんな　心配してるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,現れなかったら　どうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて世は滅ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,言ったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:01.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それは春になっても花が一輪も咲かないのと同じこと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヌシというのは理の現われだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:13.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山と理とが深く結ばれていることの証だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　ヌシの監視がなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐らく　ヌシが死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山を見てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前はここにいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が来たから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,寿命だと言ったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　まだ次のヌシが現れてない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:14.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山が不安定な間は　お前はここを動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしかして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヌシの…卵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:21.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃんと 生まれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:40.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あのヌシの力がこの中にあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺とは正反対の…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,選ばれたもの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今なら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:10.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今なら　その力を自分のものにできるんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,馬鹿な
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何を考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これ一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよう　どうしたら…
