Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:40.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,多分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:47.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あそこは行ったら戻れないところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:53.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:17:01.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もともと俺に居ていい場所なんてないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,トコヤミが暴れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止めろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:21.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何でお前は俺の邪魔ばかりするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:41.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　生きていたいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:55.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻れと言ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:05.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺は戻ってもいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:13.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ギンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:29.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコ　お前　無事か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山は当分閉じねばならんな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,理は消えてしまったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山は　どうなるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前が会ったものこそが理だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,地表に現れる花がヌシなら　彼らは根
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,彼らがヌシの命を受け取ったのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつか　またヌシは現れるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　もう旅の支度をしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺はお前を許す訳にはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう二度とお前には会わん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日はここらで休むか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:22.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう二度とお前には会わん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　忘れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:32.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この世に　居てはならない場所など誰にもない
